{"tid":813383,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"幼稚園影1000蚊一打學生相　巴打：今日去咗影16蚊","createTime":"2018-09-10T11:43:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T11:43:29.000Z","uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"897a3d198a7618111ded3bae2b6d7a9605c0fb33","tid":813383,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T11:43:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幼稚園影1000蚊一打學生相　巴打：今日去咗影16蚊</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n仲記唔記得你細個影嘅學生相？肥仔黎記得，細個影學生相，10蚊一打，求其到爆。肥仔黎嘅黑歷史，又咩嘴又半合眼！但各位巴打絲打知唔知，而家媽媽除咗注重囝囝嘅學識，仲會好重視張學生相？<br />\n最底有片！！！<br />\n以前就話，入名幼稚園要報學前面試班，入到人生就成功咗少少。但點只咁簡單，而家有家長就話幼稚園會睇囝囝嘅學生相，所以有唔少影樓都會做埋學生相生意！<br />\n<br />\n三張相入面，你鍾意邊張？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/-2018-09-07-3.48.52_15328814815b92318d5006b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F-2018-09-07-3.48.52_15328814815b92318d5006b.png&h=e7a3dd02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">428蚊一打</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/-2018-09-07-3.49.00_880177335b92318394f5b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F-2018-09-07-3.49.00_880177335b92318394f5b.png&h=266e47e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多Studio都會幫小朋友影學生相，呢一間就收428蚊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/-2018-09-07-3.49.28_2020365695b923252f2f82.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F-2018-09-07-3.49.28_2020365695b923252f2f82.png&h=29a26b92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為咗影張相，真係出盡法寶。<br />\n<br />\n好辛苦，個小朋友先笑得自然。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/-2018-09-07-3.49.44_8018737515b92329d88db5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F-2018-09-07-3.49.44_8018737515b92329d88db5.png&h=1d929273&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/-2018-09-07-4.11.46_3074414285b9232cc4bba0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F-2018-09-07-4.11.46_3074414285b9232cc4bba0.png&h=6addc3ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">980蚊一打</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/-2018-09-07-3.50.44_21182123205b92332a44b80.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F-2018-09-07-3.50.44_21182123205b92332a44b80.png&h=095ad4ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">呢一間，980蚊一打！貴到呢！唔少名人都搵佢影！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/-2018-09-07-3.50.51_18183552775b92332edfc68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F-2018-09-07-3.50.51_18183552775b92332edfc68.png&h=8ad2dd23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">為咗個小朋友笑得自然，個攝影師真係好熟練咁同小朋友玩咗好多唔同遊戲！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/-2018-09-07-3.51.20_10421362595b923337b714b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F-2018-09-07-3.51.20_10421362595b923337b714b.png&h=ac5a0f3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">引到個小朋友好開心！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/-2018-09-07-3.51.08_1672807045b9233337135d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F-2018-09-07-3.51.08_1672807045b9233337135d.png&h=9a6cb9da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">出到嚟，當然唔差！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/-2018-09-07-3.51.26_11173163365b92333cd13e3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F-2018-09-07-3.51.26_11173163365b92333cd13e3.png&h=98edae15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">老闆就話，雖然好多幼稚園都話唔睇相，但點解要交相？最後成績一樣，又會唔會睇相呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/-2018-09-07-3.52.11_6463045795b923340da906.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F-2018-09-07-3.52.11_6463045795b923340da906.png&h=c30d73db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">100蚊一打</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">出面啲普通晒相舖，好多都百令蚊一打！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/-2018-09-07-3.53.03_14567327155b923459dddd7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F-2018-09-07-3.53.03_14567327155b923459dddd7.png&h=7ac7ca5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">個職員又唔係影相出身，幫你正正經經影完就算好！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/-2018-09-07-3.53.19_13736238255b92345e22523.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F-2018-09-07-3.53.19_13736238255b92345e22523.png&h=e646786d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">最後成果，當然冇咁好！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/-2018-09-07-3.53.23_19172004345b92346228e7c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F-2018-09-07-3.53.23_19172004345b92346228e7c.png&h=4cc7822f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">你又覺得邊張靚呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/-2018-09-07-3.53.40_14878723965b9234664f8fd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F-2018-09-07-3.53.40_14878723965b9234664f8fd.png&h=d174cbbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/-2018-09-07-4.21.40_5829699305b92361c53869.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F-2018-09-07-4.21.40_5829699305b92361c53869.png&h=ee1ca028&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/-2018-09-07-4.22.00_8999581575b92361dbe1bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F-2018-09-07-4.22.00_8999581575b92361dbe1bb.png&h=c91d0b4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/-2018-09-07-4.22.15_13195380355b92361ef3213.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F-2018-09-07-4.22.15_13195380355b92361ef3213.png&h=b55e19db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/-2018-09-07-4.22.47_18725164065b9236206d508.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F-2018-09-07-4.22.47_18725164065b9236206d508.png&h=02467ac5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/-2018-09-07-4.23.58_1056651735b9236219623c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F-2018-09-07-4.23.58_1056651735b9236219623c.png&h=40b757cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/g2MFNy5pdSM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fg2MFNy5pdSM&d=cE8iLJcogGCGUKmxDnImtJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=b0bcfbcf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/g2MFNy5pdSM</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.plastichubdaily.com/41210/%E7%9C%9F%E5%BF%83%E8%86%A0/%E5%B9%BC%E7%A8%9A%E5%9C%92-%E5%BD%B1-1000%E8%9A%8A-ctla1/10/?wfc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.plastichubdaily.com%2F41210%2F%25E7%259C%259F%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%2586%25A0%2F%25E5%25B9%25BC%25E7%25A8%259A%25E5%259C%2592-%25E5%25BD%25B1-1000%25E8%259A%258A-ctla1%2F10%2F%3Fwfc&d=cE8iLJcogGCGUKmxDnImtJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=239f8be6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.plastichubdaily.com/41210/%E7%9C%9F%E5%BF%83%E8%86%A0/%E5%B9%BC%E7%A8%9A%E5%9C%92-%E5%BD%B1-1000%E8%9A%8A-ctla1/10/?wfc</a>"}]}